snippet.title: Blazing Beaks | Gameplay trailer | Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Blaze your way through dangerous arenas filled with hordes of mutants, monsters and other creepy creatures.
Discover the new rogue-lite game that will conquer your heart!

Pre-order now! ⏩ http://bit.ly/BlazingBeakseShop
